column1: Have you found work on Quora?
column3:
Yes. I have received at least 6-7 interview invitations. Apart from that;.? a get a lot of these (almost once every week) :

"We are building a platform that will take the world by storm. It is a million dollar idea. Would you like to get on board ? We are looking for talented individuals like you who can handle the technical aspects. Good money is guaranteed"

Needless to say;.? I don't even bother replying to such messages. I have also noticed a meteoric rise in number of profile views and connection requests on LinkedIn ever since I started writing actively on Quora. I can recall at least 2 very genuine invitation from good startups offering me a role that I think might have suited me.

So yes;.? Quora might actually help you discover exciting career opportunities.

Edit : This answer was written on a positive note. I should add that I didn't accept any invitations. Moreover;.? it was pretty evident from my LinkedIn and Quora profile that I am new grad fresh out of college who is actively seeking job opportunities. I do not think experienced developers will have much advantage from Quora - at least not at the time of writing this answer.

Sarajevo;.? 29. april 2016. (MINA) – Danas je reisu-l-ulema Islamske zajednice u Bosni i Hercegovini Husein ef. Kavazović uputio čestitku povodom nastupajućeg pravoslavnog blagdana Vaskrsa Episkopu zahumsko-hercegovačkom i primorskom Grigoriju.

„Povodom nastupajućeg blagdana Vaskrsa Vama i vjernicima pravoslavne vjere upućujem iskrene čestitke. Želim da Vam blagdani donose radost i novu nadu u bolje razumijevanje i sretniju budućnost za sve nas“;.? stoji između ostalog u čestitki reisu-l-uleme Kavazovića.

column1: Reisu-l-ulema primio dr. Alwi Shihaba i Tan Sri dr. Abdullah Bibn Muhammad Zin
column3:

Reisu-l-ulema Kavazović se i ovom prilikom zahvalio ovim prijateljskim zemljama iz Jugoistočne Azije i njihovim narodima koji su pružili i pružaju svesrdnu pomoć našem narodu i našoj domovini.
